{"tid":759816,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★加綜援有望！調查指有基層兒童及青少年營養不足 促設營養援助計劃","createTime":"2018-07-29T03:50:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-29T04:03:01.000Z","uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"546a5521b52e2966851e716ec4c0db5afa0abe1c","tid":759816,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T03:50:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/29/114930_ecdf188b64b6502bf527486a5606fa0b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F29%2F114930_ecdf188b64b6502bf527486a5606fa0b.png&h=a6bcb683&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/29/114931_35569d31913456f67a366c253bb131f7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F29%2F114931_35569d31913456f67a366c253bb131f7.png&h=2b750956&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一項調查顯示基層兒童及青少年飲食營養不足，有兩成受訪者有時需要挨餓。  民社服務中心在今年一至六月，訪問了216名六至十七歲基層兒童及青少年。發現超過八成受訪者，在肉類和奶類的攝取，未能達衞生署建議的標準，亦有近八成受訪者五穀類、蔬菜類的攝取不達標。有近兩成受訪者表示在金錢不足下「要捱餓」和「食少餐」。  中心建議設立營養援助計劃，讓基層家庭有能力購買營養食物。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.tvb.com/local/5b5d3029e60383487fe936ad/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.tvb.com%2Flocal%2F5b5d3029e60383487fe936ad%2F&d=%2BE7Kq8wY7GpSYtDHNsGSHPjR1yQ20Y%2BboumAcDwsk0E%3D&h=68eb7236\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.tvb.com/local/5b5d3029e60383487fe936ad/</a>"},{"pid":"b0663033bb64d836c2f986d5b7e1b1814a87e35b","tid":759816,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T03:52:36.000Z","msg":"咁支那肥蝗有冇得減綜援<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5360d740ba72e4b8b83234298fa939dc03216f68","tid":759816,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T03:53:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/07/29/StWFRo.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=h